snippet.title: Tonka Dig N Rigs Commercial
snippet.description: This here is the commercial for Tonka Dig N Rigs, one of those Tonka PC games I owned as a kid. Ripped off another YouTube vid on the Toonami commercial break in 2000. Enjoy.
